OL,5, Some debt management companies are     
OL,6, receiving payments for passing clients 
OL,7, on to insolvency practitioners, a BBC  
OL,8, Disclosure investigation has found.    
OL,10,FIt also found some companies were      
OL,11,Fmaking money from entering people into 
OL,12,Fthe wrong debt solutions and pushing   
OL,13,Fthem further into financial hardship.  
OL,15,FThree years ago, Cassandra Naylor was  
OL,16,Fraising three young children on her own
OL,17,Fand was struggling to cope.            
OL,19,FShe ran up thousands of pounds of debt 
OL,20,Fas she tried to make ends meet.        
